From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: JP Simard <jp@jpsim.com>
Date: Fri, 2 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Bump iOS platform to v12

The Iterable swift-sdk Package.swift declares iOS 10 but the source
uses iOS 12+ APIs (e.g. NWPathMonitor). Bump the declared platform to
match what the source actually requires so it compiles correctly when
the package's declared minimum is applied as the build's minimum OS.
---
 Package.swift | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Package.swift b/Package.swift
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/Package.swift
+++ b/Package.swift
@@ -4,7 +4,7 @@ import PackageDescription

 let package = Package(
     name: "IterableSDK",
-    platforms: [.iOS(.v10)],
+    platforms: [.iOS(.v12)],
     products: [
         // The external product of our package is an importable
         // library that has the same name as the package itself:
